Text: How are the new digsPST Cooper I hope your move on the weekend went well How are you liking the new digs I read the Powers report on Enron on the weekend basically just checking for my name didnt find it One of the highlights was the fact that in one of the many deals with the partnerships Enron actually bought put options on Enron stock I hope things go well at UBS My number is Ill probably give you a shout re poker sometime in Feb not sure when though Bill
